        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This <em>specialist's ring</em> is dedicated to the evocation school of magic, and the ring is covered in symbols and glyphs related to the evocation school according to the creator's arcane studies. You gain a +2 item bonus to Arcana checks, and a +1 circumstance bonus to recognize magical effects and items of the evocation school of magic.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">f</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You gain 1 Focus Point, which you can use only to cast a wizard school spell of the evocation school. If not used by the end of your turn, this Focus Point is lost.</p>"
